FBIS4-57787 "drlat101_i_94001" FBIS-LAT-94-101 Daily Report 24 May 1994 Nicaragua Government Backs UN, OAS Measures Against Haiti Government Backs UN, OAS Measures Against Haiti PA2405184694 Managua Sistema Nacional de Television Network in Spanish 0200 GMT 24 May 94 PA2405184694 Managua Sistema Nacional de Television Network in Spanish 0200 GMT 24 May 94 Spanish BFN [From the "National Newscast"] [Text] A Nicaraguan Foreign Affairs Ministry statement maintains that Nicaragua, as a UN member, is backing the measures adopted by the UN Security Council against Haiti's de facto military government, which is ruling that country. Nicaragua also backs the OAS measures and flatly rejects the human rights violations by the coupist military leadership.
